<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-61-1214 </DOCNO><TEXT>A series of improvements to a blast furnace in an Italian iron and steelplant have been carried out to improve energy efficiency. In additionto the improvements in hardware, a microprocessor based control systemhas been installed. Results are presented of its operational experienceand the payback for the whole scheme is likely to be between 4 and 7years. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>